{"tid":567928,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逐粒抽出來！港交所字牆 貶義字貼晒label","createTime":"2018-02-21T09:49:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-21T14:01:07.000Z","uid":39464,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d94881e8536195e9744624b33a788d5af85b0a6a","tid":567928,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T09:49:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180221/large/1519206258_d3a8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180221%2Flarge%2F1519206258_d3a8.jpg&h=73830952&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港交所（388）新交易大堂的字牆上出現多個貶義字，引來網民猛烈抨擊，今日本報記者再度前往港交所，發現有人將字牆上的貶義字逐一貼上label紙，例如「貪、貧、敗」均有貼紙，未知是否想更換牆上的貶義字。對此港交所暫未回覆。<br />\n<br />\n新交易大堂昨日開幕，門口設計有中幅「字牆」，由「貝」字的中文漢字設計而成，但昨晚被網民及知名Blogger恥笑，字牆上印有「賊」、「贓」「賄」、「賂」、「賤」、「殯」、「敗」、「貪」、「貧」等貶義字，諷刺港交所品味庸俗，更指設計像骨灰龕，引發公關災難。<br />\n<br />\n知名Blogger徐少驊在fb出Post，指港交所最新的Wall Design，更向網民表示，「大家看到『關公』的影子嗎？」，牆除了印有「贏」、「賺」、「賞」等傳統褒義字外，亦有「賊」、「贓」，「賄」、「賂」等字，被網民恥笑港交所設計庸俗有問題，更有人揶揄港交所應該用簡體字取悅內地人。亦有網民認為設計像骨灰龕：「好有由墳墓爬出來的氣氛！十足骨灰罈的佈景，外觀看起來很陰森可怖囉！」<br />\n<br />\n本報曾就此事向港交所查詢，其回覆指港交所無參與選擇牆上選取的字，完全交由策展商中國金融博物館設計；港交所認為貝殼是中國最早嘅貨幣，所以有貝字旁嘅漢字大多與貨幣、金錢相關，與金錢相關嘅字，意義不一、有正有反，正如金錢帶來嘅禍福難料。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180221/57856505\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180221%2F57856505&d=QTcD7cvUk5BaeGQS6jHlGgEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=ee684e95\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180221%2F57856505&h=8a36bf7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180221/57856505</a>"},{"pid":"ac01789d441e51b2ffd6db291d55be8b4e0f63f4","tid":567928,"uid":58852,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T09:53:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">所以有貝字旁嘅漢字大多與貨幣、金錢相關，與金錢相關嘅字，意義不一、有正有反，正如金錢帶來嘅禍福難料。</span><br />\n我覺得解得幾好喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23b9300388dc14da4349ba804afa80de836d0afc","tid":567928,"uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T09:53:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本報曾就此事向港交所查詢，其回覆指港交所無參與選擇牆上選取的字，完全交由策展商中國金融博物館設計</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n果然係支那STYLE！<br />\n<br />\n388奶支奶到雪雪聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e02d8515e15dfaf435ca039193647a0335147273","tid":567928,"uid":18292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac01789d441e51b2ffd6db291d55be8b4e0f63f4","tid":567928,"uid":58852,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T09:53:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">所以有貝字旁嘅漢字大多與貨幣、金錢相關，與金錢相關嘅字，意義不一、有正有反，正如金錢帶來嘅禍福難料。</span><br />\n我覺得解得幾好喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T09:56:29.000Z","msg":"咁咪唔好拆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3f4aa23c6cc7588a0d04c6448896c6b9ee00d9e","tid":567928,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e02d8515e15dfaf435ca039193647a0335147273","tid":567928,"uid":18292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac01789d441e51b2ffd6db291d55be8b4e0f63f4","tid":567928,"uid":58852,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T09:53:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">所以有貝字旁嘅漢字大多與貨幣、金錢相關，與金錢相關嘅字，意義不一、有正有反，正如金錢帶來嘅禍福難料。</span><br />\n我覺得解得幾好喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T09:56:29.000Z","msg":"咁咪唔好拆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T10:29:12.000Z","ms